NOTE — the `ml` detector uses the Magi v2 model (ragavsachdeva/magiv2), which is
distributed under its own custom, NON-COMMERCIAL license (personal, research,
and not-for-profit use only; commercial use requires the author's permission).
manga-panels does not redistribute the model — it is downloaded at runtime — but
using `--detector ml` is subject to Magi's terms. The default `xycut` detector
carries no such restriction. See https://huggingface.co/ragavsachdeva/magiv2
